    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2>《能准点下班吗？》是一款由单人开发，角色扮演解谜类的国产独立游戏。<br>游戏中你将扮演一名打工人，准备在六点下班时，却遇到了一系列阻止你准点下班的职场闹心事。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2>游戏中展示了现实职场中打工人深恶痛绝的一些现象：下班后开会，职场PUA，福报，画饼......<br>还有领导们喜欢说的那些温馨（逆天）言论，打工人面对这些现象应该如何应对？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/1dda21aa9f9ba82857bbfbc9ad4bc4c6.avif?t=1727515488\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/771a7e16055c192d2699930fb2f9b412.avif?t=1727515488\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/29a8632410ee2b36481938d0713c8822.avif?t=1727515488\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>游戏中你需要解开一个个由<strong>汉字</strong>组成的机关，<strong>偏旁，分裂，移动，多音字......</strong><br>体验中华文化的独特魅力！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/deeb6659e67d8a173c0f4dd7ee434fd2.avif?t=1727515488\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/4ecdc48c2198c47a65b41fdf9ca1d3e1.avif?t=1727515488\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><strong>最后，愿全天下的打工人都能 朝九又晚五，双双又休休！</strong>",
